Subject: Windows server permission scan bulk import failed
Description: Bulk import is getting failed for both domain NHY and GLOBAL permission scan. Attached document for reference.
Solution_Comment__c:
1. Dropped the T2 databases for the affected hosts and Proxies and rerun the FSAA-System Scans and Bulk Import jobs
2. Resolved issues with the reports by deleting "Reports" folder of the FSAA-Bulk Import.
